OL,3,CReport highlights record number of
OL,4,CScots facing hunger and hardship
OL,6,FFigures released by the Trussell Trust
OL,7,Fhas showcased that a record number of
OL,8,FScots are facing hunger and hardship.
OL,10,FThe poverty charity, that has
OL,11,Ffoodbanks in the south of Scotland,
OL,12,Fhave highlighted that a record number
OL,13,Fof Scots are struggling to afford food.
OL,15,FAlmost 700,000 Scots are facing hunger
OL,16,Fand hardship with almost 200,000
OL,17,Fchildren included in that figure.
OL,19,FThe research has showcased that the
OL,20,Fnumber of people facing these issues
OL,21,Fis up 24% from two decades ago.
