OL,3,CReport highlights record number of
OL,4,CScots facing hunger and hardship
OL,6,FThe Trussell Trust say that one in six
OL,7,Fchildren in Scotland are at risk of
OL,8,Fusing a foodbank.
OL,10,FThe research has highlighted that
OL,11,Falmost half of the people who are
OL,12,Ffacing hunger and hardship come from a
OL,13,Ffamily where at least one person
OL,14,Fworks. More than half of people were
OL,15,Fliving in a family with someone who
OL,16,Fhas a disability.
