OL,3,CReport highlights record number of
OL,4,CScots facing hunger and hardship
OL,6,FCara Hilton, senior policy and public
OL,7,Faffairs manager with the charity in
OL,8,FScotland, said: "We welcome the
OL,9,FScottish Government's ambition to end
OL,10,Fthe need for food banks, but our
OL,11,Fresearch shows that a record number of
OL,12,Fpeople in Scotland now face hunger and
OL,13,Fhardship.
OL,15,F"If we are to shift this dial and if
OL,16,Fthe Scottish Government is to achieve
OL,17,Fits own child poverty targets then
OL,18,Fcurrent actions to tackle hunger must
OL,19,Fbe significantly scaled up and much
OL,20,Fbetter resourced.
