OL,3,CReport highlights record number of
OL,4,CScots facing hunger and hardship
OL,6,F"In its upcoming budget, we would urge
OL,7,Fthe Scottish Government to increase
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Child Payment to #40 a
OL,9,Fweek and increase investment into
OL,10,Faffordable housing and into crisis
OL,11,Fsupport, through the Scottish Welfare
OL,12,FFund.
OL,14,F"And with larger families most at risk
OL,15,Fof hardship, the Scottish Government
OL,16,Fshould act to mitigate the two-child
OL,17,Fcap in Scotland."
