OL,3,CReport highlights record number of
OL,4,CScots facing hunger and hardship
OL,6,FSocial Justice Secretary Shirley-Anne
OL,7,FSomerville said: "No one should have
OL,8,Fto compromise on food or other
OL,9,Fessentials.
OL,11,F"We are taking forward nine actions
OL,12,Fover three years (2023-2026), to
OL,13,Fimprove the response to crisis, using
OL,14,Fa cash-first approach so that fewer
OL,15,Fpeople need to turn to food parcels."
